  <name>Marqen</name>
  <summary>Clean local document editor</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      Marqen is a clean local document editor for writing polished notes, guides, and documents with automatic formatting.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Clean writing interface with automatic formatting</li>
      <li>Tables, links, images, lists, and math expressions</li>
      <li>Export documents for sharing</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
